[SN]TITLE[SN]
Sports Direct's Mike Ashley before MPs: In quotes

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Sports Direct's Mike Ashley has been grilled by MPs about the working practices at his firm after a series of allegations.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
